====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[grow]] [[weak]]; to [[decrease]] in [[strength]]; to [[decline]]
#: {{zh-x|未老先衰|to decline in health before becoming old}}
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese|Hakka|Min}} to have [[bad]] [[luck]]
#: {{zh-x|人 衰 行路 打 倒 褪|when luck is bad, you can’t even walk straight|C}}
#: {{zh-x|衰 足 五 年|had five years of completely bad luck|C}}
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese|Hakka}} [[bad]]; [[detestable]]; [[awful]]
#: {{zh-x|咁 衰 㗎{gaa4}！|That's awful!|C}}
#: {{zh-x|咁 衰 都 有！|How can it be this awful!|C}}
#: {{zh-x|做 衰 嘢|to do '''bad''' things|C}}
#: {{zh-x|衰人|'''bad''' person|C}}
#: {{zh-x|衰婆{po4-2}|bitch|C}}
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese}} to make a [[grave]] [[mistake]]
#: {{zh-x|我 衰 咗 啦！|I've made a mistake!|C}}
#: {{zh-x|今次 唔 可以 再 衰 㗎喇 ！|(We) can’t screw it up anymore this time|C}}
#: {{zh-x|我 衰 咗 三 年，我 等 緊 個 機會，爭 返 口氣。|I had suffered three years of bad luck, I’m waiting for my turn to get everything back. (In context: spent three years in jail)  |C|ref='''1986''', {{lw|zh|英雄本色 (1986年电影)|英雄本色|''A Better Tomorrow''|pref=《|suf=》}}}}
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese|transitive}} to [[mess up]] (something); to be [[caught]] for (wrongdoing)
#: {{zh-x|你 衰 咩 呀？|What did you '''do wrong'''?|C}}
#: {{zh-x|我 衰 邊 範 啫？|What’s my wrongdoing/offence (often with legal implications)?|C}}
#: {{zh-x|衰十一|to '''get caught for''' sex with a minor|C}}
#: {{zh-x|衰 販毒|to '''get caught for''' drug trafficking|C}}
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese}} to [[suffer]] from faulty personality traits or habits, or commit minor faults with moderate to significant consequences.
#: {{zh-x|都 係 我 衰 心軟。|I had been too kind-hearted/forgiving.|C}}
#: {{zh-x|成日 衰 遲到。|He messes up all the time for being late.|C}}
#: {{zh-x|我 就 係 衰 在 太 靚仔。|My wrong is being too handsome.|C}}

